Features
No physical tables created — fully in-memory.
Partition-level comparison between old and new tables.
Computes:
Row counts
Min/Max key values
Null counts
Aggregated row checksum
Produces PASS/FAIL per partition for instant validation.
Fully dynamic — works with any table, any key column, and any partition column.
FULL OUTER JOIN ensures missing partitions in either table are flagged as FAIL.
This is a complete production-ready validation block that you can use after any batch or partitioned migration to verify data correctness without moving or duplicating data.